1. *Pivo* je obavezno na svadbama. (Beer is a must at weddings.)
2. *Piva* se uz svečanu trpezu. (Beer is drunk with a festive meal.)
3. Oči mog psa sijaše kada je čuo da ćemo otići u kafanu da popijemo *pivo*. (My dog's eyes shone when he heard that we were going to a pub to have a beer.)
4. On je došao do kraja uz muziku i *pivo*. (He reached the end with music and beer.)
5. Ona nije voljela da pije *pivo*, ali je pristala da pije pivo s nama. (She didn't like drinking beer, but she agreed to have a beer with us.)